dct_description_sm: Map shows population density, in individuals per square mile, and percentage of absentees among able-bodied males for each district. Areas of tsetse fly presence are also shown. Original map is filed in the Map and Geospatial Information Center. A map reproduction is attached to companion volume. Crown copyright reserved. Map is number 2.
